# TypeScript interfaces and types (`types/`)

- Shared `export interface` / `export type` → repo-root **`types/`**; import **`app/types/...`**
- One domain module per feature; brief JSDoc (see **`types/I_appMenusDataList.ts`**)
- No colocated **`<filename>.types.ts`** under **`src/`**, **`src-electron/`**, **`.storybook-workspace/`**, **`helpers/`**
- Ambient augmentations → **`types/`**; side-effect import from owning boot or **`src/stores/index.ts`** (see **`types/piniaModuleAugmentation.ts`**)
- No shim modules that only re-export types from **`app/types/...`**
- Managers/stores/barrels export values only; consumers import types from **`app/types/...`**
- ESLint **`types-folder/no-exported-types-outside-types`** on **`**/*.{ts,vue}`** outside **`types/**`**, **`**/*.d.ts`**, **`i18n/**`**

## Naming

- **`I_`** interfaces, **`T_`** type aliases; **`i18n/`** uses **`L_`**

## Level-1 `functions/`

- **`import type`** from **`app/types/**`** only ([fa-two-level-architecture.mdc](fa-two-level-architecture.mdc))
